Package: gp3bayes
Title: Contract-First Bayesian Workflows for Hierarchical Behavioural Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(
      given = "Stefanos",
      family = "Balaskas",
      email = "s.balaskas@ac.upatras.gr",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2444-9796")
    )
Description: Provides transparent, contract-first infrastructure for Bayesian
    analysis of repeated-measures and hierarchical behavioural data. It
    supports explicit model contracts, readiness audits, deterministic
    simulation and preparation for hierarchical binary outcomes, inspectable
    prior specifications, prior predictive checks, and restricted optional
    fitting of approved binary models through 'brms' and 'rstan'. Core
    validation and specification remain backend-independent and require no
    compiler, hardware-specific export, or external dataset.
